The paper focuses on developing techniques for detecting manipulated face images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning architectures, which is a common topic in the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
